<text top="2191" left="170" width="954" height="62" font="font1" id="p1_t34" reading_order_no="33" segment_no="27" tag_type="list">¢  The  extent  to  which  the  level  of  accuracy  impacts</text>
<text top="2244" left="202" width="871" height="63" font="font0" id="p1_t35" reading_order_no="34" segment_no="27" tag_type="list">an  individual’s  reaction  to  the  privacy  infringe-</text>
